rows.label: tlk70000138_10_msg0001
rows.name:
Felt time to come home to
the capital for a while.

rows.label: tlk70000138_10_msg0002
rows.name:
Things have been rough lately. I
was worried about my old man.

rows.label: tlk70000138_10_msg0003
rows.name:
But it seems you lot helped
him out while I was away.

rows.label: tlk70000138_10_msg0005
rows.name:
When I went to see him he was
still indifferent to me...

rows.label: tlk70000138_10_msg0006
rows.name:
He said a quick hello and then went
right back to his inventions.

rows.label: tlk70000138_10_msg0007
rows.name: Ah, well. Maybe that'll never change.
